{"tid":1439774,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[全世界入黎]要令中間派歸邊，首先要做思想革命","createTime":"2019-08-10T08:22:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T10:35:54.000Z","uid":300391,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"70b3e92af1aec685d486e8629634cf36bc487c67","tid":1439774,"uid":300391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:22:45.000Z","msg":"成日講香港一亂就搞彎經濟，影響民生，其實搞革命既人都知，咁點解仲要搞？<br />\n<br />\n香港既優勢：基本法「港人<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">治</span></span></strong>港，高度自治。」<br />\n<br />\n要管<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">治香港</span></span></strong>，需要三權：行政權、立法權及司法權，並且要三權分立，互相制衡。<br />\n<br />\n2014年，831人大落閘&mdash;小圈子選特首，香港人已經失去<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">行政權</span></span></strong>，所有施政方針，已被<strong>[size=]<span style=\"color: red;\">中央強行奪走</span>[/size=4]</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n應屆立法會選舉，本土派立法會後選議員及當選民主派議員被無理取消資格，親中派成功佔據立法會大部份議席，再加上立法會議事規則修改，令立法會主席權力過大，間接令<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">立法權斷送中央</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">自由</span></span></strong>，建基於<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>司法制度既保護</strong></span>。中央已經奪去管治香港既行政及立法權，當下既司法權亦不斷受到衝擊，包括：人大兩次釋法、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">逃犯修訂修例</span></strong>、廿三條立法，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">意圖矮化司法權，令三權失衡，</span></strong>而令香港人與生俱來既自由抹殺。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人要做既係革命，所謂既革命係推翻現有既選舉制度，推行真正既民主制度，將三權還於香港市民，重奪香港既優勢，「港人治港，高度自治。」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n否則，三權歸中，等於基本法玩完，繼而走資，香港經濟跟住大倒退，民不聊生。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c463dbfee4647e8be994fc136eb46eadcebecfb","tid":1439774,"uid":300391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:28:54.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"3874d698aeec76580025ec38bf557f90d33c2712","tid":1439774,"uid":300391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:30:19.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"1d072f971b13160634232a22dee41d9e573378a8","tid":1439774,"uid":300391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:36:08.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"4a3c5dc7c217037a4854826d5e1200ea7f5101ab","tid":1439774,"uid":300391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:49:11.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"6e124c96a78599f38017913d654b66dbf9389e4e","tid":1439774,"uid":300391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:05:30.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"f8f89fb8a1e2461098161a4e8844297a325ba873","tid":1439774,"uid":300391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:47:23.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"b3d94349f6de8533a93c11e6aac725e4f1844272","tid":1439774,"uid":300391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:58:02.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"10bd69e53df0ab595102fcb5ac221b49feb83cd8","tid":1439774,"uid":300391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:15:09.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"de22d5192dea800c7fcb9152a1f3f9aa91e89cdd","tid":1439774,"uid":300391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:21:41.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"83e4fea6f8b3e7f81842b16f50da919e14f60349","tid":1439774,"uid":300391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:35:54.000Z","msg":"1"}]}